
  SCM Postprocessing Tools

CONTENT

  Fortran 90 Programs

    post_1d.f90              Visualization tool based on gnuplot.
    chvct.f90                Change vertical coordinates in forcing file
    chua.f90                 convert forcing file:  unformatted <-> formatted
    f2grads.f90              convert forcing file to grads binary+ctl file

  Fortran 90 modules

    mo_system.f90          define system routines
                           (external or module subroutines)
    mo_1d_io.f90           read or write the forcing file
    ask_module.f90         manage dialog with user
    unit_number_module.f90 Fortran unit number bookkeeping
    mo_grads.f90           write grads files

  Makefile                 Makefile
  ab_ecmwf_32              Example vertical coefficient table (32 Levels)

INSTALLATION

  Fortran Programs:

    Type 'make' within this directory. The executables 'post_1d', 'chvct',
    and 'chua' will be placed in the ../../data directory
